84
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:36,400
OK.

85
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:37,080
Good.

86
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:40,320
Don't keep anything from me.

87
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,000
OK.

88
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:41,600
Rest assured.

89
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,720
See you next time, then.

90
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:44,040
OK.

91
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,440
Bye-bye.

92
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,120
Hei.

93
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,960
Shanshan is clever.

94
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:55,680
My advice is

95
00:05:55,930 --> 00:05:56,920
don't keep it from her.

96
