548
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:51,760
You two both did well.

549
00:25:52,080 --> 00:25:52,800
So great.

550
00:25:52,800 --> 00:25:53,880
Looks awesome.

551
00:25:54,480 --> 00:25:55,160
Liu.

552
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:57,000
Come here.

553
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:57,960
Coming.

554
00:25:58,040 --> 00:25:59,200
Don't mind us.

555
00:25:59,200 --> 00:25:59,960
